<table border="0" height="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="1007" style="background:url(images/bg1.jpg)" align="center">
<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	道教“三清”源流探微
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">石衍丰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;当我们步入神州大地的道教宫观时，多数宫观内有座&ldquo;三清殿&rdquo;，是宫观建筑的中心，殿内供奉着&ldquo;三清尊神&rdquo;即元始天尊、灵宝天尊、道德天尊，那么&ldquo;三清&rdquo;在道教中的含义及其流变如何，这是本文试图探讨的问题。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;三清&rdquo;就其文义的神学内涵来看，&ldquo;清&rdquo;是受中国古代文化传统影响，即&ldquo;清气为天，浊气为地&rdquo;而来的，&ldquo;清&rdquo;在这里实指&ldquo;天&rdquo;。至于为什么用&ldquo;三&rdquo;来表述&ldquo;清&rdquo;，而不是其它数字，仔细分析主要原因有二<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">首先，道教基本经典《道德经》的&ldquo;道生一，一生二，二生三，三生万物&rdquo;，是采用&ldquo;三&rdquo;的教理依据。道教早期经典《太平经》的《和三气兴帝王法》，则进一步发挥了&ldquo;三&rdquo;的教理思想，称</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;元气有三名，太阳、太阴、中和。形体有三名天、地、人。天有三名日、月、星，北极为中也。地有三名为山、川、平土。人有三名父，母、子。治有三名君、臣、民。欲太平也，此三者常当腹心，不失铢分，使同一优，合成一家，立致太平，延长不疑矣。&rdquo;①从这些文献资料中可以找到用&ldquo;三&rdquo;命名&ldquo;清&rdquo;</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">即天</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">的教理依据。其次确有受佛教&ldquo;三身&rdquo;、&ldquo;三世&rdquo;说的影响。南宋哲学家朱熹曾指出</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;道家之学，出于老子，其所谓三清盖仿释氏三身而为之尔。&rdquo;②我们</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">并不完全赞同朱子的这一看法，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">③</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">但也不能完全否认道教&ldquo;三清神&rdquo;的出现，曾受佛教&ldquo;三身&rdquo;说的影响。又《灵宝斋仪》有三世天尊之说，&ldquo;过去高上玉皇天尊，未来太极天尊，见<font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">现</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">在元始天尊&rdquo;④。正是由于上述两个方面的原因，道书有&ldquo;三一为宗&rdquo;之说，&ldquo;合三以为一，散一以为三，道之要&rdquo;⑤。&ldquo;夫三一者，盖乃智照无方，神功不测，恍兮为像，金容玉质之姿，窈兮有精，混一会三之致。因为观景，则开众妙之门，果用成德，乃极重玄之道。&rdquo;又云&ldquo;三一者，神、气、精；希、微、夷；虚、无、空。&rdquo;⑥正是在这类宗教理论思想指导下，道教以&ldquo;三&rdquo;命名&ldquo;清&rdquo;，这仅是个人的一孔之见。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;三清&rdquo;从道教神学的视角来看其内涵又是什么呢<font face="Times New Roman">?</font><font face="宋体">道书认为</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;三清者，言三清净土无杂染秽，其中宫主，万绪千端，结气凝云，因机化现，不可穷也。&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑦</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">很明显，&ldquo;三清&rdquo;在道教神学里包含内容有二<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">所谓&ldquo;三清净土&rdquo;是指&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;是天神所居之胜境，全称是玉清圣境在清微天，上清真境在禹余天，太清仙境在大赤天。&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;的系统是大罗天、三清天、四种民天</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">四梵天</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">、无色界四天，有色界十八天，欲界六天，共三十六天。三界二十八天则仿佛教而来。&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;又有&ldquo;三清为金宫、上清为火宫、太清为土宫&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑧</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，或称&ldquo;紫微宫、紫霞宫、紫晨宫&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">⑨</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。另外，还有&ldquo;三清者，人之三田也&rdquo;⑩。所谓&ldquo;其中宫主&rdquo;，是指住在&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;的神仙，最高的三位至上神，亦称&ldquo;三清&rdquo;，它们是元始天尊<font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">又称玉清大帝</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">、灵宝天尊</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">又称太上大道君、上清大帝等</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">、道德天尊</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">又称太上老君、混元老君、降生天尊、太清大帝等</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">。三清神仙的系统是，太清仙境有九仙，即上仙、高仙、大仙、玄仙、天仙、真仙、神仙、灵仙、至仙，上清真境有九真，玉清圣境有九圣，真圣之号亦以上、高、大、玄、天、真、神、灵、至为次第。&ldquo;三清&rdquo;的这两个内涵，从道教历史发展来看，是先出现&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;，后有三位至上神住在三清境，尤以唐宋以来宫观建筑的中心是&ldquo;三清殿&rdquo;，供奉元始天尊、太上大道君、太上老君三位尊神，因此，也称&ldquo;三清&rdquo;或&ldquo;三清神&rdquo;。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;三清&rdquo;之称，始于何时，从现有比较明显可以断代的文献资料有两个方面<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">一是&ldquo;三清&rdquo;一词最早见于南朝宋、齐道教思想家顾欢的赋诗言志</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;五塗无恒宅，三清有常舍，精气因天行，游魂随物化&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;</font></span><span>11</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">又梁文学家、史学家沈约<font face="Times New Roman">(441-513)</font><font face="宋体">赠道教学者陶弘景的《酬华阳陶先生》称</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;三清未可觌，一气且空存，所愿回光景，拯难拔危魂，若蒙九丹赠，岂惧六龙奔。&rdquo;</font></span><span>12</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">以及沈约撰《桐柏山金庭馆碑》写道<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;夫三清者，若夫上元奥远，言象斯绝，金简玉字之书，元霜降雪之宝，俗士所不能窥，学徒不敢轻慕&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;</font></span><span>13</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。顾欢对&ldquo;三清&rdquo;的解释是&ldquo;常舍&rdquo;，沈约是&ldquo;未可视&rdquo;、&ldquo;不能窥&rdquo;，而道教学者梁陶弘景所撰《洞玄灵宝真灵位业图》，虽编列了七个中位的约五百多的庞大的神仙谱系，仍未明确&ldquo;三清神&rdquo;。从顾、沈、陶他们的著述综合分析，我们可以断定，在南朝时&ldquo;三清&rdquo;所指是&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;。二是《魏书&middot;释老志》载<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;又言二仪之间有三十六天，中有三十六宫，宫有一主，最高者无极至尊，次日大至真尊，次天覆地载阴阳真尊，&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;。这条史料表明两点</font><font face="Times New Roman">:1.</font><font face="宋体">于道教三十六天中有三清天，可证北魏时已出现&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;。</font><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;宫有一主&rdquo;虽已明示&ldquo;三清天&rdquo;内亦有主，但其最高者神名与元始天尊等有差异。至此，上述两个方面的文献资料足以断定，&ldquo;三清&rdquo;一词最早出现在南北朝时，仅指&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;由上可知，&ldquo;三清&rdquo;先是&ldquo;境&rdquo;，从&ldquo;境&rdquo;如何又有尊神的含义呢<font face="Times New Roman">?</font><font face="宋体">从我们现已接触文献资料，大概有几条线索可供研究。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;首先，是随着道教&ldquo;三洞&rdquo;说的流行后</span><span>14</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，以&ldquo;三清妙境乃三洞之根源，三宝之所立也&rdquo;</span><span>15</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，逐步形成的。道书称<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;但知洞真法天宝君住玉清境，洞玄法灵宝君住上清境，洞神法神宝君住太清境。故《太上苍元上录经》云</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">三清者，玉清、上清、太清也。&rdquo;</font></span><span>16</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">由此可见，&ldquo;三洞&rdquo;、&ldquo;三宝君&rdquo;和&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;的联结，是&ldquo;三清&rdquo;从&ldquo;境&rdquo;向&ldquo;尊神&rdquo;含义扩展的一座桥梁。又如《九天生神玉章经》称<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;天宝君则大洞之尊神&rdquo;，其注&ldquo;天宝君则玉清元始天尊也&rdquo;。&ldquo;灵宝君者则洞玄之尊神&rdquo;，其注&ldquo;灵宝君上清天尊也&rdquo;。&ldquo;神宝君者则洞神之尊神&rdquo;，其注&ldquo;神宝君太清天尊也。&rdquo;</font></span><span>17</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">此注为华阳复所注，概在宋代以降。据我们所知，&ldquo;三宝尊神&rdquo;开始并非&ldquo;三清尊神&rdquo;可称&ldquo;三洞尊神&rdquo;。这里也有两条资料可证<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">唐武宗时</font><font face="Times New Roman">(841-846)</font><font face="宋体">的一次道教神灵排列，先为元始天尊、太上大道玉晨君、太上老君</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">此即三清尊神</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">，其后列有&ldquo;玉清大有天宝君，上清妙玄灵宝君，太清太极神宝君三宝尊神&rdquo;。</font></span><span>18</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">金大定七年<font face="Times New Roman">(1167)</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;中都十方大天长观&rdquo;中的飞玄阁&ldquo;以秘道藏，兼奉三天宝君</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">清微天宝君、禹余灵宝君、大赤神宝君</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">&rdquo;</font></span><span>19</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，在进一步的发展中，是以元始天尊牵头，将&ldquo;三宝君&rdquo;、&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;、&ldquo;三洞&rdquo;相联结，基本上完成了&ldquo;三清&rdquo;由&ldquo;境&rdquo;向&ldquo;尊神&rdquo;含义的扩展。据《业报经》《应化经》并云<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;天尊曰</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">吾以道气，化育群方，从劫到劫，因时立化。吾以龙汉元年号无形天尊亦名天宝君，化在玉清境，说洞真经十二部以教天中九圣，大乘之道也。&hellip;&hellip;吾以延康元年号无始天尊亦名灵宝君，化在上清境，说洞玄经十二部以教天中九真，中乘之道也。&hellip;&hellip;吾以赤明之年号梵形天尊亦名神宝君，化在太清境，说洞神经十二部以教天中九仙，小乘之道也。&rdquo;</font></span><span>20</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这里的&ldquo;三宝君&rdquo;成为元始天尊在&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;的别名，这是&ldquo;三清&rdquo;从&ldquo;境&rdquo;向&ldquo;神&rdquo;扩展的主导线索。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;其次，上述所引《魏书&middot;释老志》已有明示，三十六天有三十六宫，宫有一主，当然也表明&ldquo;三清天&rdquo;内亦各有一主，这是不言而喻的。又《元始上真众仙记》称<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;玄都玉京七宝山，&hellip;&hellip;在大罗之上&hellip;&hellip;有上、中、下三宫。&hellip;&hellip;上宫是盘古真人元始天王、太元圣母所治。中宫太上真人金阙老君所治。下宫九天真皇、三天真王所治。&rdquo;这些资料所述，与&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;、&ldquo;三清神&rdquo;均有些瓜葛，虽不显著，但作者认为它对道教各派最终供奉&ldquo;三清&rdquo;为至上神，担任了各自的角色。唐《老君圣纪》载</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;此即玉清境元始天尊，住在三十五天之上也&rdquo;，&ldquo;此即上清境太上大道君，住在三十四天之上也&rdquo;，&ldquo;太清境太极宫即太上老君，住在三十三天之上也。&rdquo;</font></span><span>21</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这里的&ldquo;三清尊神&rdquo;是元始天尊、太上大道君、太上老君，已经很明确了。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;第三，从道教宫观建筑演变的视角，也可提供&ldquo;三清&rdquo;从&ldquo;境&rdquo;向&ldquo;神&rdquo;扩展的线索。道教初创时五斗米道的&ldquo;二十四治&rdquo;，其&ldquo;治&rdquo;建筑中心是崇虚堂或崇玄台。南北朝至唐初，宫观建筑中心是&ldquo;天尊殿<font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">堂</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">&rdquo;</font></span><span>22</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，它表明当时是以元始天尊为最高神。至于&ldquo;三清殿&rdquo;的建造，根据目前所见文献资料，如陈垣先生编《道家金石略》的唐代碑刻表明，道士、道民从贞观到开元年间<font face="Times New Roman">(627-741)</font><font face="宋体">敬造的主要是元始天尊像，其中还记有&ldquo;开成中</font><font face="Times New Roman">(836-890)</font><font face="宋体">始诏赐号三清之观。&rdquo;在《龙角山记》的《庆唐观碑铭》、《重修三清殿记》中所修三殿，其一曰老子殿</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">玄元殿</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">，次曰三清殿，次曰三皇殿。这些文献资料表明，&ldquo;三清殿&rdquo;在唐代已建造，对于&ldquo;三清&rdquo;从&ldquo;境&rdquo;向&ldquo;神&rdquo;的扩展中，无论从&ldquo;境&rdquo;与&ldquo;神&rdquo;的紧密结合，或在社会上广为传播方面，都会有着明显的促进作用。总之，&ldquo;三清&rdquo;含义从&ldquo;境&rdquo;向&ldquo;神&rdquo;扩展的三条线索是在相辅相成中逐步完成的。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;三清&rdquo;源流发展线索大致如上所述。围绕着与&ldquo;三清&rdquo;有关的尊号，南宋道教学者金允中的《上清灵宝大法》卷<font face="Times New Roman">22</font><font face="宋体">，也有所总结。&ldquo;三尊之号在经中只称元始天尊、太上道君、太上老君</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">其别号曰天宝君、灵宝君、神宝君，以三境之名而称之则曰</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">玉清、上清，太清</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">以三洞之书而名则曰洞真、洞玄、洞神，如此而己。&rdquo;由此可见，作为&ldquo;三清&rdquo;从其本义来说是作为&ldquo;天&rdquo;、&ldquo;境&rdquo;，天上有&ldquo;三清天&rdquo;、&ldquo;三清境&rdquo;住着元始天尊、灵宝天尊、道德天尊</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">地上的道教宫观有&ldquo;三清殿&rdquo;，殿内元始天尊塑像居中，左为灵宝天尊、右为道德天尊的塑像，它是宋代以降道教宫观建筑之中心，一直保留至今。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;至于三清尊神的形成，从道教历史的发展是有一个较为没长而又复杂的历程，当东汉末年五斗米道初创时奉太上老君为至上神，魏晋南北朝时的《上清》、《灵宝》经出现，又有元始天王、元始天尊、太上玉晨大道君、太上大道君等新的道教尊神。鉴于各派新出现的众多神仙，梁陶弘景应客观需要撰《洞玄灵宝真灵位业图》，三清尊神的雏形已基本确立，经过各派进一步融合、协商，提出&ldquo;道不可无师尊，教不可无宗主，故老君师太上玉晨大道君焉，大道君即元始天尊之弟子也&rdquo;</span><span>23</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的共识，正是这种师徒关系，使它们成为三位一体的&ldquo;三清尊神&rdquo;。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;三清尊神&rdquo;还有&ldquo;说经教主元始天尊，抱送玉帝道君<font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">灵宝</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">天尊，流演圣教降生</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">道德</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">天尊。&rdquo;</font></span><span>24</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;元始乃道中之祖为灵宝祖师，道君乃法中之祖为宗师，老君乃教中之祖为真师&rdquo;</span><span>25</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">等职能分工不同的解释。若以出现为序，先为&ldquo;老君&rdquo;，次为&ldquo;元始&rdquo;，再为&ldquo;道君&rdquo;。此外，五代闽主供奉&ldquo;三清&rdquo;为宝皇大帝、天尊、老君。</span><span>26</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">今成都青羊宫三清殿内壁画，有&ldquo;阴三清&rdquo;，即骑九头锦毛狮子者为救苦天尊<font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">居中</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">，骑白鹤者为吕纯阳祖师</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">居右</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">，乘龙者为汉钟离祖师</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">居左</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span>27</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;注<font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;①王明《太平经合校》<font face="Times New Roman">19</font><font face="宋体">页。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;②《朱子语类》<font face="Times New Roman">125</font><font face="宋体">卷《论道教》。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;③参见拙作《道教神系渊源之管见》载《宗教学研究》<font face="Times New Roman">1990</font><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Times New Roman">1-2</font><font face="宋体">期。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;④《一切道经音义妙门由起》引《灵宝开天经》。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;⑤《云笈七签》卷<font face="Times New Roman">11</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;⑥《云笈七签》卷<font face="Times New Roman">49</font><font face="宋体">引《玄门大论三一诀》。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;⑦《云笈七签》卷<font face="Times New Roman">6</font><font face="宋体">《三洞经教部&middot;三洞并序》。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;⑧《洞玄灵宝自然九天生神王章经解》卷上。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;⑨《云笈七签》卷<font face="Times New Roman">720</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;⑩《修真太极混元图》。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>11</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《南史》卷<font face="Times New Roman">75</font><font face="宋体">《顾欢传》。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>12</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《古今图书集成》神异典卷<font face="Times New Roman">218</font><font face="宋体">《道教部&middot;艺文二》。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>13</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《古今图书集成》神异典卷<font face="Times New Roman">281</font><font face="宋体">《道观部&middot;艺文一》。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>14</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">拙作《道教&ldquo;三洞&rdquo;源流识微》载《上海道教》<font face="Times New Roman">1989</font><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Times New Roman">1-2</font><font face="宋体">期。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>15</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《云笈七签》卷<font face="Times New Roman">6</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>16</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《道教义枢》卷<font face="Times New Roman">21</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>17</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《洞玄灵宝自然九夭生神不章经注》卷土。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>18</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《无上黄箓大斋立成仪》卷<font face="Times New Roman">15.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>19</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《宫观碑志&middot;中都十方大天长观重修碑》。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>20</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《云笈七签》卷<font face="Times New Roman">6</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;三洞并序&rdquo;。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>21</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《要修科仪戒律钞》引《太真科》。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>22</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《洞玄灵宝三洞奉道科戒营始》《置观品》。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>23</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《犹龙传》卷<font face="Times New Roman">1</font><font face="宋体">《启师资》。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>24</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《高上玉皇满愿宝忏》《玉皇宥罪消福宝忏》。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>25</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">宁全真《土清灵宝大法》卷<font face="Times New Roman">l0</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>26</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《资治通鉴》卷<font face="Times New Roman">282</font><font face="宋体">《后晋王纪》。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>27</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">此壁画为<font face="Times New Roman">1988-1989</font><font face="宋体">年间由成都青羊官住持张元和率众弟子敬立，信士熊北雁敬绘。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
